{"tid":2454262,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK ROSÉ SOLO出道隊友們都送禮應援啦！Jennie送的毛絨小花真的超像ROSÉ","createTime":"2021-03-20T05:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T10:04:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c566dea0f32d07c0814d9104abbbae3fe96582af","tid":2454262,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_984623aa724cafc7769f9568e1fd1d2b/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-17/134319-900369.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_984623aa724cafc7769f9568e1fd1d2b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-17%2F134319-900369.png&h=6e9687c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK的甜酷女孩ROS&Eacute; Solo出道，《On the ground》強勢來襲。<br />\n<br />\nROS&Eacute; 的嗓音極具磁性柔美，語音感超強，被粉絲們稱為「澳洲野玫瑰」。 作為四代女團的實力主唱，ROS&Eacute;首張專輯的成績也非常矚目。 預售後的四天時間便突破了40萬張的銷量，創下歷史新高和記錄。 而她還刷新了公開24小時內就在YouTube上創下4160萬點擊率的K-POP SOLO新紀錄，前一位紀錄保持者還是PSY。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3f9c1563504d17cce17d73bac2943b9d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-17/134319-900370.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3f9c1563504d17cce17d73bac2943b9d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-17%2F134319-900370.png&h=1f069e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好隊友solo出道，團魂滿滿的BLACKPINK其他成員怎麼能不為她應援呢。 Jennie送上了和ROS&Eacute; 的氛围很像的毛絨小花，粉色的花朵山點著兩個小眼睛，非常可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ewe8KL1U8AAN4kB?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEwe8KL1U8AAN4kB%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=f2cf4302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ewe8KL1VEAAtvSF?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEwe8KL1VEAAtvSF%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=c4763729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJISOO則送上了親手製作的糖果，是想要讓ROS&Eacute;吃糖迅速補充能量，好在舞台上大方光彩嗎？ R字棒棒糖大到幾乎和ROS&Eacute;的臉一樣了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EwekqcxUYAI2QeM?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEwekqcxUYAI2QeM%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=450c477e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLisa更是親自到場，捂著臉一臉「嬌羞」，被ROS&Eacute;攻氣十足地抱著，原來是Lisa沒有化妝不好意思露臉啦。 Lisa還給ROS&Eacute;送上了美麗的花花，感情真的好好呀！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/roses_are_rosie/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Froses_are_rosie%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=15a02208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/roses_are_rosie/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n「圖：IG@roses_are_rosie、推特@@roses_are_rosie、@blackpinkbabo」"},{"pid":"0fcc2cb82dd6f1ab3e9c522a56824f6caa1834c6","tid":2454262,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:57:55.000Z","msg":"冇人理...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022680fceb99c51b4fd2c4dbc54aabb7cc074dfa","tid":2454262,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"}]}